<li>Karatu to the Serengeti - 2 to 3 hours by private vehicle</li>
<li>The Serengeti to Karatu - 2 to 3 hours</li>
<li>Karatu to Arusha via the Ngorongoro Rim - 2.5 hours by private vehicle</li>
<li>Arusha to Zanzibar - 1.5 hour flight</li>
